# Component Design Rules

React components must follow a clear structure.

Component responsibilities must be separated into:

UI
State
Logic

---

# Component Structure

Each component should follow this structure:

component/
├ Component.tsx
├ Component.styled.ts
├ Component.test.ts
└ index.ts

---

# Component Principles

Components must follow the Single Responsibility Principle.

Components must not contain large business logic.

Business logic should be moved to:

features/
model/
hooks/

---

# Component Naming

Component names must be clear and descriptive.

Examples:

LoginForm
UserCard
ProductList
